        "description": {
            "name": "description",
            "type": "java.lang.String",
            "value": "The default values that are returned when calling getPathInfo(), getBaseUrl(), etc. from Zend_Controller_Request_Http are empty strings rather than being auto-detected based on the actual request.  This causes Zend_Controller_RewriteRouter->route() to try to match based on an incorrect value for $pathInfo.  The attached patch fixes this."
        },
